    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A small but very powerful and respected clan of the Hidden Stone. They possess a strong bloodline and one of its founding member was the first Tsuchikage . They constitute a major trump card of the village&#x27;s defense and have strong connection in its military.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Yachoumaru Clan.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Core</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 8+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 2 from Chakra Control, Climb, Genjutsu, Hide, Investigate, Jump, Knowledge (ninja lore), Knowledge (tactics), Ninjutsu, Survival, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Advanced Bloodline (Dairiki), Chakra Affinity, Defensive Martial Arts, Genin, Nin Weapons Proficiency, Ninjutsu Adept, Taijutsu Adept.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Affiliation:</b> You require 1 less success to learn Yachoumaru Hijutsu techniques.</p>"
